These are the DaCHS resource descriptors of the data centre at
Fesenkov Astrophysical Institute.

This is intended to be cloned into DaCHS' rootdir as inputs, something
like this::

  cd /var/gavo
  rmdir inputs
  git clone git@github.com:ill-i/fai-inputs.git inputs

You will then need to do a few symlinks into the common datastore.
TBD: do we give the commands to do that here or in each individual repo.
